## PRIORITY 5 — EVENT LISTENER ISSUES

### 49. All four listeners swallow exceptions — retries never happen
**Files:**
- `backend/app/Listeners/ConsumeLoyaltyHoldListener.php` ~lines 47-53
- `backend/app/Listeners/EarnPointsFromOrderListener.php` ~lines 56-64
- `backend/app/Listeners/ReleaseLoyaltyHoldListener.php` ~lines 37-45
- `backend/app/Listeners/DeductInventoryListener.php` ~lines 41-47

**Problem:** All catch `Throwable` and log instead of re-throwing. This defeats the `$tries = 3` retry mechanism. Loyalty holds are never consumed, earned points are lost, inventory drifts.
**Fix:** Re-throw the exception after logging so the queue worker retries. Optionally add a `failed()` method for dead-letter handling.

